OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cthe death of a woman in Exeter
OL,6,FDetectives have started a murder
OL,7,Finvestigation after the death of an
OL,8,Felderly woman in Exeter.
OL,10,FOfficers were called to an address on
OL,11,FMillbrook Lane, Exeter, at around
OL,12,F12.40pm on Sunday 19 April because of
OL,13,Fconcerns over the welfare of the woman.
OL,15,FOfficers and paramedics attended, and
OL,16,Fthe woman was pronounced deceased at
OL,17,Fthe scene. Enquiries are ongoing to
OL,18,Ffind her next of kin.
