OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776708666
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cthe death of a woman in Exeter
OL,6,FAn elderly man from Exeter has been
OL,7,Farrested on suspicion of murder and is
OL,8,Fcurrently in police custody.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Guy Biggar, who is
OL,11,Fleading the investigation, said:
OL,12,F"Officers are carrying out enquiries
OL,13,Fto establish what happened and a
OL,14,Fcordon has been set up to allow for a
OL,15,Fthorough investigation of the scene.
OL,17,F"It is believed that the man and the
OL,18,Fwoman were known to each other.
OL,26,@tD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
