OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1776708666
OL,3,CMurder investigation underway after
OL,4,Cthe death of a woman in Exeter
OL,6,F"I would like to reassure the
OL,7,Fcommunity that this is being treated
OL,8,Fas an isolated incident, and we are
OL,9,Fnot seeking anyone else in connection
OL,10,Fto the death.
OL,12,F"Members of the public will see an
OL,13,Fincreased police presence in the area,
OL,14,Fand we would encourage anyone, if they
OL,15,Fhave any concerns, to contact officers
OL,16,Ffrom the local neighbourhood policing
OL,17,Fteam."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@FO]
